1. *Pošteno* se trudim da greške ne ponavljam.(I honestly try not to make mistakes again.)
2. Uvek je *pošteno* odgovarala na moja pitanja.(She always answered my questions honestly.)
3. Kupila je *poštenu* cenu za taj proizvod.(She bought a fair price for that product.)
4. Ona je *poštena* i časna osoba.(She is an honest and honorable person.)
5. On je *pošteno* radio na tom projektu.(He worked honestly on that project.)